{"tid":2312492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林超英：「明日大嶼」工程是無需要亦造成破壞","createTime":"2020-12-05T04:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T11:51:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":128,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"88d217b1d29f75c71c187f54d409a626aba651c7","tid":2312492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"天文台前台長林超英，在社交網站發文，批評立法會財委會昨日通過明日大嶼工程5.5億元前期研究撥款，令人失望，質疑工程無需要，亦會造成破壞。 <br />\n<br />\n林超英認為工程並無科學需求，指土地供應專責小組假設香港未來人口達920萬，但統計處最新推算人口在2039年高峰只有810萬，相差超過100萬，多於人工島的人口容量。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，大規模填海建造人工島，將會令香港成為全中國在自然保育方面最落後的地方，同時違反《生物多樣性公約》對保護生物多樣性的要求，令香港蒙羞，亦令作為公約締約國的中國蒙羞。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2369429&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=65224e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369429</a>"},{"pid":"ae9f0fc027f4a102717c04220fb85c1e721e23ee","tid":2312492,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"國安法"},{"pid":"fbb0039b3d7aa1d8ace4b5e73ad6daaa97e9b064","tid":2312492,"uid":76804,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"林超英居然反政府<br />\n搵國安拉佢啦<br />\nbtw你覺得宜家填海真係為左香港人?<br />\n統計署果個stat<br />\n未計黎緊政府究竟會做幾多野輸入大量支那人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3403d126d3a9a6ca09c8b07de4856a44a64aa0c","tid":2312492,"uid":62837,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"支持起 最好起到爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b62360092b818b257aac18fd72f83d60135055","tid":2312492,"uid":267395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"得啦 執定包袱啦 再唔走港共就唔承認你本BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmo